vote.title: Authorize a two-year consultant contract, with two one-year renewal options for the comprehensive reform of the Dallas development codes, Chapters 51, 51A, and 51P for the Department of Planning and Urban Design - Camiros, Ltd, most advantageous proposer of four - Not to exceed $2,015,660 - Financing: Operating Carryover Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
